title: ETH v1 Listing: Add MIM market
body:
Intro: This is a vote to list MIM on C.R.E.A.M. ETH v1 market with a Collateral Factor and Collateral Cap.

Proposal: Listing Committee

Rational: Add stable coin with strong community

For: 
Add MIM market with Collateral Factor: 90% and Collateral Cap: $50M

Against: 
Do not make any changes to ETH v1 market.
author: 0x81f8CaBe89066d43EB4faFD8E4E5256C102E6E30
